text_content: The render folder that is trying to be created is unable to be created. This can be a general windows problem as if a process has stalled when trying to create a directory, it can be seen as "open" by other processes.   It could also point to permission issues.  Please pass this over to Systems Administrators

text_content: Plugins are effects and that "plugged in" to nuke EG. Mocha pro.  These plugins need to exist on all machines in order to render.
